https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/1.7/topics/i18n/translation

* Translation files are located in <language>/LC_MESSAGES/django.po.
* For local development, set the fully qualified path for LOCALE_PATHS in your local_settings.py 

# If translation strings are added, changed or deleted, re-makemessages
./manage.py makemessages -l es --ignore="ve" --ignore="login.html" --ignore="password*.html" --ignore="registration*.html"

# Then, compile them
./manage.py compilemessages

# Then, checkin the resulting .mo file
